
            

            <p>I see a word in buffer1. I want to look for it in buffer2.  I select the word in buffer1. I select buffer2 as my current buffer, hit <code>C-s</code>, and press <code>mouse-2</code> (the middle mouse button).</p>

<p>Emacs converts the word to lowercase, and I can't find it...  The word has both lower and upper cases in it. How can I prevent Emacs from downcasing the search pattern?</p>

<p>I am using Emacs version 23.1.1 on RHEL 6.</p>

        